{"tid":330764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★新同事自願OT 打工仔呻做壞規矩","createTime":"2017-07-21T13:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T11:28:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d8fb88161ce9e06bb4ae4ba0574060250707c7e2","tid":330764,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"每次到新公司上班，都要適應新人事新作風，初來甫到若不懂同事間的潛規則，隨時會得罪人。有網民指新同事總會最早返工，下班又遲遲不離開，因「自願OT」而得罪同事。有學者指，新人宜主動了解新公司的辦公室文化，有助融入新環境。<br />\n<br />\n有打工仔於論壇上發表帖文，指同事之間向來習慣每天工作九小時，夠鐘便準時下班，事主形容新來的同事「唔知博乜，日日最早到係佢，最遲走又係佢，自願OT（加班工作）？」直指新同事「做壞規矩」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民對有關情況似是見慣不怪，留言指「新嚟永遠都係咁」。亦有網民估計，新同事可能只是責任感強，工作態度不同或效率較慢，甚至可能經歷過前上司不喜歡他太準時放工，才會自願留下工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1862496/%E6%96%B0%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E8%87%AA%E9%A1%98OT%20%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E5%91%BB%E5%81%9A%E5%A3%9E%E8%A6%8F%E7%9F%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1862496%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E9%25A1%2598OT%2520%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%2591%25BB%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25A3%259E%25E8%25A6%258F%25E7%259F%25A9&d=4M8BOIEz%2FIHvV4HK%2B5aQaDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f32b91b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1862496/%E6%96%B0%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E8%87%AA%E9%A1%98OT%20%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E5%91%BB%E5%81%9A%E5%A3%9E%E8%A6%8F%E7%9F%A9</a>"},{"pid":"c988591abc0502cd50a8c50f1cacaa4f10a45502","tid":330764,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:48:09.000Z","msg":"蓋老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e13d3d5afb95f8afb0afd997e2990f9adcf56d1","tid":330764,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:05:47.000Z","msg":"OT又插，唔OT又插，晴報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0038130576cd8cf5fdbe1cc018cca79e0c89f9","tid":330764,"uid"